# Test Fixture for Markdown Files

This document contains various references to dev-* paths that should be updated.

## Documentation Links

- See [Tools Documentation](dev-tools/docs/README.md)
- Check out the [Handbook](dev-handbook/index.md)
- Review [Current Tasks](dev-taskflow/current/)
- Local configuration in [dev-local/config.yml](dev-local/config.yml)

## Inline References

The `dev-tools/` directory contains all executable tools. You can find templates in `dev-handbook/templates/` and manage tasks in `dev-taskflow/`.

Local overrides are stored in "dev-local/" directory.

## Code Blocks

```bash
cd dev-tools/
./bin/tool --help

# Navigate to handbook
cd ../dev-handbook/
ls -la

# Check taskflow
cd ../dev-taskflow/current/
cat README.md

# Local config
cp template.yml ../dev-local/config.yml
```

```ruby
require 'dev-tools/lib/tool'
load 'dev-handbook/lib/helper.rb'
Dir.glob('dev-taskflow/**/*.md')
File.read('dev-local/settings.yml')
```

