- URL style: file://dev-local/cache/data.json

## Mixed Contexts

The project structure includes "dev-tools/" for tools, 'dev-handbook/' for documentation, `dev-taskflow/` for tasks, and dev-local/ for local settings.

### Nested Paths

- Main: dev-tools/lib/dev-tools/core.rb
- Docs: dev-handbook/docs/dev-handbook/overview.md
- Tasks: dev-taskflow/current/dev-taskflow/structure.md
- Local: dev-local/cache/dev-local/temp.txt